text: William Jones (29 September 1928 - 16 August 2017) was a Canadian sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2017 deaths Category:Canadian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Canada Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
